{"tid":418762,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後竟然連自熱火鍋都未食過，衝住係客面前丟哂架！","createTime":"2017-09-30T00:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T05:52:55.000Z","uid":19334,"like":16,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"862ecf3dd58848e42222edac6d62537c31e66d80","tid":418762,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:09:33.000Z","msg":"話說就黎中秋，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地公司有funding for 約舊客食下飯，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁有個客係隻90後一路跟開，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咪孖住佢一齊出去食飯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我地約左個客去高級酒店食自助餐，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如是者就傾下計，傾下野食！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n傾到打邊爐，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個客問我地有無試過好熱門果隻自熱火鍋，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小妹好小淘寶買野食都有食過，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當我正想答佢既時候，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻90後衝住出黎丟架話：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「見過人地食，自己未食過！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住個客笑左一笑，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問隻90後係咪住深山，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁熱門既野食都架食過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢獲真係乜野架都比佢丟哂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25568329804fc9c26f5a5324388a52672d8f55ee","tid":418762,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 90後"},{"pid":"d0054be40a5355f91d4f7dbaaab91ce95cdd72ce","tid":418762,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:11:55.000Z","msg":"唔係話針對，但肯定係講緊班90後"},{"pid":"c0b72460a14443ecbc7ea197b034f12efd6c7059","tid":418762,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 90後</blockquote><br />\n恨鐵不成鋼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f795a2c38243d32845dda62051fbf4970d3cabd","tid":418762,"uid":58413,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:33:15.000Z","msg":"乜係自熱火鍋？<br />\n<br />\n利申：70後"},{"pid":"066a9a5fa13c90a4a7c51bed66d8f812c06ccbc3","tid":418762,"uid":18321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:37:33.000Z","msg":"60分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273008102149f23f85296fc6f793b7e983705676","tid":418762,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T00:51:38.000Z","msg":"自瀆火煱?"},{"pid":"b6d010a1d3713ef4c6bb4cf18eb7845935c7da75","tid":418762,"uid":68736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:13:06.000Z","msg":"清好波"},{"pid":"a81eddf1ca4f7b669f6bbf68e74a9d17f8d2a672","tid":418762,"uid":143783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"乜嘢自熱"},{"pid":"51422d34ccb55839ef3454f093ff28c58da993b3","tid":418762,"uid":10231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:51:38.000Z","msg":"置業火鍋"},{"pid":"3be63aabba9373e550c4344cd5676fa89770df7d","tid":418762,"uid":143783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>置業火鍋</blockquote><br />\n聽到忽然有點心up"},{"pid":"07e0206ebca05ceede3464c6c7a8f98a22d92b1a","tid"